00:14:03.110 --> 00:14:06.200
I did a great job giving Senpai his lunch!

00:14:06.200 --> 00:14:09.240
How do you like my raw talent <i>now</i>, huh?

00:14:09.240 --> 00:14:10.660
Nice!

00:14:09.660 --> 00:14:11.120
"November 3"

00:14:10.660 --> 00:14:12.990
Keep it up.

00:14:12.990 --> 00:14:16.830
They'd get together faster
if it weren't for this nonsense...

00:14:25.130 --> 00:14:27.010
Almost there!

00:14:29.800 --> 00:14:32.260
Aw, <i>man</i>!

00:14:32.260 --> 00:14:34.970
That was a great race!

00:14:34.970 --> 00:14:38.100
You move well now
that you've got the hang of it.

00:14:38.100 --> 00:14:41.860
--Thanks for playing another
new game with me, Yanagi.

00:14:41.860 --> 00:14:43.440
--Hana always finds this
kind of fun versus-play games
--Thanks for playing another new game with me, Yanagi.

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:47.360
