00:14:47.360 --> 00:14:51.450
--to practice with me
before she takes on her senpai.
--Why don't I cook one of your favorite meals tomorrow? What would you like?

00:14:51.450 --> 00:14:53.030
Gratin!

00:14:53.030 --> 00:14:58.160
She may be my sister and all,
but she shows love in a warped way.

00:14:54.950 --> 00:14:56.410
