00:14:58.160 --> 00:15:00.870
Your senpai likes gaming, too, doesn't he?

00:15:00.870 --> 00:15:05.420
Yeah, but he always
goes for one-player titles.

00:15:05.420 --> 00:15:08.260
I've gotta introduce him
to this kind of game, too.

00:15:08.260 --> 00:15:09.880
Huh.

00:15:09.880 --> 00:15:12.300
Sure wish I could meet him!

00:15:12.300 --> 00:15:13.600
No way.

00:15:13.600 --> 00:15:16.020
Oh, right. I've got a report to write.

00:15:16.020 --> 00:15:18.430
Aw, Hana! You always do this.

00:15:18.430 --> 00:15:22.060
C'mon, Hana! Aw, c'mon!

00:15:22.060 --> 00:15:26.110
There she goes, running off again.
Such a hardhead.

00:15:26.110 --> 00:15:29.070
Why does she hate the idea so much?

00:15:29.070 --> 00:15:34.580
Whatever her reasons,
if Hana's gonna stay clammed up,

00:15:34.580 --> 00:15:36.620
I've got an idea of my own.

00:15:36.620 --> 00:15:40.500
Oh, my--you're all smiles!
What is it, Yanagi?

00:15:40.500 --> 00:15:42.500
Right, Mom?

00:15:47.710 --> 00:15:50.420
I overslept!

00:15:50.420 --> 00:15:55.140
Oh, Yanagi! You're up early
for a Sunday. Heading out?

00:15:55.140 --> 00:15:56.310
Well, you know.

00:15:56.310 --> 00:15:57.470
Nice!

00:15:57.470 --> 00:15:58.890
You've got work?

00:15:58.890 --> 00:16:00.730
Yep! See you later!

