00:16:28.960 --> 00:16:30.380
Hello.

00:16:32.590 --> 00:16:38.140
Hi, I'm Uzaki's little sister Yanagi.
Thanks for everything you do for her.

00:16:38.140 --> 00:16:39.430
Well, well!

00:16:39.430 --> 00:16:42.180
Y-Yanagi?! I thought you were heading out!

00:16:42.180 --> 00:16:44.230
Yeah, I was.

00:16:44.230 --> 00:16:45.480
I did.

00:16:46.770 --> 00:16:48.190
How did you...?

00:16:48.190 --> 00:16:50.570
I asked Mom.

00:16:52.240 --> 00:16:57.410
Don't go blaming her--I only
asked her where you worked.

00:16:57.410 --> 00:17:02.040
It's fine, right? Not like
I quizzed her about your senpai.

00:17:02.040 --> 00:17:03.620
Go home!

00:17:03.620 --> 00:17:08.500
Hey, now. Don't be chasing off
your sister when she's come all this way.

00:17:08.500 --> 00:17:12.920
The morning rush just ended,
so you can take your time and relax.

00:17:12.920 --> 00:17:14.470
Sit anywhere you like.

00:17:14.470 --> 00:17:17.340
He's huge... must be him!

00:17:18.100 --> 00:17:20.310
It's just, um, you know...

00:17:20.310 --> 00:17:23.730
I don't like having friends
and family watch me work--

00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:23.640
"November 29"

00:17:23.730 --> 00:17:26.900
I get all flustered,
and it's hard to do my job!

00:17:26.900 --> 00:17:32.570
Feels like I've said the
exact same thing to someone...

00:17:32.570 --> 00:17:33.740
At any rate,

00:17:33.740 --> 00:17:38.280
I'll handle clean-up;
you wait on your sister.

00:17:38.280 --> 00:17:39.740
Thanks...

00:17:42.750 --> 00:17:46.870
I kinda figured you had
some kind of reason

00:17:46.870 --> 00:17:51.380
for suddenly taking this job
your second year of college...

00:17:51.380 --> 00:17:52.920
Was I right?

00:17:57.630 --> 00:18:01.060
One hot cafÃ© au lait, boss.

00:18:01.060 --> 00:18:02.510
Got it.

00:18:02.510 --> 00:18:07.100
What's wrong?
You were fine when Ms. Tsuki came.

00:18:03.350 --> 00:18:08.060
"Lousy Cat Wants to Hang Out!"

00:18:07.100 --> 00:18:08.940
"Ms. Tsuki"...

00:18:08.940 --> 00:18:10.480
What?

00:18:10.480 --> 00:18:12.360
Nothing.

00:18:12.360 --> 00:18:15.740
Look, she can be a real handful.

00:18:17.200 --> 00:18:18.610
What is it?

00:18:18.610 --> 00:18:21.330
Just... you have a little sister.

00:18:21.330 --> 00:18:23.040
What's wrong with that?!

00:18:23.040 --> 00:18:26.410
I'm not messing with you or anything.

00:18:26.410 --> 00:18:30.540
You look after me,
worry about me in weird ways,

00:18:30.540 --> 00:18:33.250
even fuss over me sometimes--

00:18:33.250 --> 00:18:35.920
and now I know why.

00:18:35.920 --> 00:18:39.180
It's like... I get it now.

00:18:41.350 --> 00:18:43.180
What's <i>that</i> about?

00:18:43.180 --> 00:18:45.680
Huh... so you're a big sister.

00:18:45.680 --> 00:18:48.190
Are you <i>sure</i> you're not messing with me?

00:18:48.190 --> 00:18:51.360
I'm sure. I'm an only child, see?

00:18:51.360 --> 00:18:54.070
I don't know the trials
of being an older sister.

00:18:54.070 --> 00:18:55.360
How about that...?

00:18:55.360 --> 00:18:56.610
You're totally messing with me.

00:18:56.610 --> 00:18:58.450
I am not.

00:18:59.610 --> 00:19:01.320
Really?

00:19:01.320 --> 00:19:03.030
Yes, really.

00:19:06.540 --> 00:19:09.420
Your cafÃ© au lait's ready.

00:19:10.750 --> 00:19:12.380
Thanks!

00:19:12.380 --> 00:19:18.090
As long as I keep Senpai far away
from her, I can make it through this day.

00:19:18.090 --> 00:19:22.640
If I serve Yanagi... and guard him...

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:25.180
Then I'll grill her back home.

00:19:25.930 --> 00:19:28.180
Here's your cafÃ© au lait!

00:19:28.180 --> 00:19:30.270
Hey, can your senpai serve--

00:19:30.270 --> 00:19:33.400
Your table's been assigned to <i>me</i>.

00:19:34.150 --> 00:19:37.530
I will <i>not</i> let those
two have a conversation.

00:19:37.530 --> 00:19:39.820
C'mon, Uzaki.

00:19:39.820 --> 00:19:45.330
You forgot to give her a hot towel--and
after she came here in this cold.

00:19:45.330 --> 00:19:46.620
Here you are.

00:19:47.240 --> 00:19:51.210
Thank you very much!
My fingertips were cold.

00:19:51.210 --> 00:19:53.710
Why are you just
earnestly doing your job?!

00:19:53.710 --> 00:19:56.340
You're mad at me for being thoughtful?

00:19:56.340 --> 00:20:00.840
Oh, would you be Hana's senpai, then?

00:20:00.840 --> 00:20:02.720
Can we talk for a moment?

00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:03.890
Yanagi!

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:08.470
Sure, why not?
We don't have any other customers.

00:20:08.470 --> 00:20:10.180
Senpai!

00:20:10.180 --> 00:20:14.100
I... I have to stop them.
At this rate, I just know...

00:20:14.100 --> 00:20:20.030
Hana's told me so much about you.
I wanted to see you for myself!

00:20:20.030 --> 00:20:20.900
Is that so?

00:20:20.900 --> 00:20:23.200
Senpai, Senpai! You have work to do!

00:20:23.200 --> 00:20:24.990
Nah, I'm caught up.

00:20:24.990 --> 00:20:26.200
Dammit!

00:20:26.200 --> 00:20:29.330
For as much as you suck at cooking,
you sure are quick to tidy up!

00:20:29.330 --> 00:20:33.620
I can never tell if you're
complimenting me or mad at me...

00:20:33.620 --> 00:20:36.420
How old are you, Mr. Senpai?

00:20:36.420 --> 00:20:38.800
Twenty-one. And you, miss?

00:20:38.800 --> 00:20:39.920
Eighth grade.

00:20:39.920 --> 00:20:42.840
Huh! You're more put-together than Uzaki--

00:20:42.840 --> 00:20:45.090
I was sure you were
at least in high school.

00:20:45.090 --> 00:20:48.010
--Um...
--Wow, really?

00:20:48.010 --> 00:20:49.060
Absolutely.

00:20:49.060 --> 00:20:50.890
Well, we better be getting back...

00:20:50.890 --> 00:20:55.440
Oh, right: I heard you play
a lot of games, Mr. Senpai.

00:20:55.440 --> 00:20:57.690
Actually, so do I!

00:20:57.690 --> 00:20:59.530
You do?

00:20:59.530 --> 00:21:00.900
Have you played that one game?

00:21:00.900 --> 00:21:01.990
Which one?

00:21:01.990 --> 00:21:05.320
<i>Final Quester:</i>
<i>Tales of Pocketter ~Lousy Catter~.</i>

00:21:05.320 --> 00:21:08.990
The one with all the "-er"s! Yeah, yeah!

00:21:08.990 --> 00:21:12.250
That opening cutscene was so darn long.

00:21:12.250 --> 00:21:13.580
It really was!

00:21:13.580 --> 00:21:18.090
And after its super-cool,
drawn-out climax rendered in amazing CG,

00:21:18.090 --> 00:21:21.800
your first real quest is
to gather medicinal herbs!

00:21:21.800 --> 00:21:24.840
Kinda dampens the ol' enthusiasm.

00:21:24.840 --> 00:21:26.970
You got that right.

00:21:26.970 --> 00:21:31.220
--Uh-oh. Now their chat's all animated.
--At least you get a horse to ride on.

00:21:31.220 --> 00:21:34.480
Who saw <i>this</i> turn of events coming?

00:21:34.480 --> 00:21:37.690
--So, miss, when you played--
--Oh, Mr. Senpai?

00:21:37.690 --> 00:21:41.530
You don't have to call me "miss."

00:21:41.530 --> 00:21:46.820
You can call me by
my first name. It's Yanagi.

00:21:46.820 --> 00:21:50.280
Eh? Okay, then... Yanagi-<i>chan</i>.

00:21:53.500 --> 00:21:56.330
See?! I <i>knew</i> this was going to happen!

00:21:57.250 --> 00:21:59.290
"The last wild goose becomes first."

00:21:59.290 --> 00:22:04.420
Meaning: That which comes from
behind to surpass those up ahead.

